com.varmateo.yawg.api

Class Result<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.varmateo.yawg.api.Result<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the value in a success result.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Result.Failure, Result.Success

    public abstract class Result<T>
extends Object
    Represents the success or failure of an operation. A success has an associated value. A failure has an associated cause.
